description: Botanica By Air Wick Wax Candle Caribbean Vetiver & Sandalwood is a wax candle blended with natural ingredients. Nature inspired. Planet conscious.Air Wick Candle Caribbean Vetiver & Sandalwood is a blend of natural and paraffin waxes. Fragrance infused with responsibly sourced natural ingredients. Great fragrance from first to last burn. Lasts up to 40 hours. Nothing but the ingredients you needFragrance- Infused with essential oilsHelpers - Natural and naturally derived wax and paraffin wax- Fuels the flameMicrocrystalline wax- Helps maintain a stable productUV stabiliser- Prevents discolourationWe've partnered with WWF so we can help protect and restore native wildflowers.Learn more at Botanica.airwick.com.au and Botanica.airwick.co.nzTogether for Wildflower Habitats.Responsibly sourced natural ingredients.Great fragrance: Infused with essential oils.Free from dyes.Burns for up to 40 hours.
